data.description: This move-in ready home features luxurious modern touches throughout! You'll find gorgeous backsplash in the kitchen, LVP and tile flooring, sleek fireplace in the living room, a large soaking tub in the master bathroom, and a shaded back patio just to name a few! Enjoy the extra bedroom or entertaining space that the BONUS ROOM provides! Just a short drive to all the local conveniences such as the hospital, restaurants, and shopping! This listing will go fast! Call to schedule a viewing today!!
